Courtesy of one very talented (and blindfolded) 7 year old. 😂 We’re calling this the #IAmSparkella Challenge and we want to see how you and your kid(s) do! Upload your videos to Instagram using the hashtag and tagging me and @Sparkella. Can’t wait to see ‘em and maybe share some. Also head over to my story in a sec to vote on who wore it better… 🦄 #Sparkella

node.text: This is only 1/16 how long this went for hahaha she an animal. We love wrestling and boxing. And we keep it fun. I heard once that martial arts was only created to take the mystery out of fight. So people started to practiced it. So if ever there came a time they had to defend themselves they wouldn’t be as afraid. In my experience fear most times leads to bad decisions. Being calm and secure with your mind and body...Make great opportunity for good decisions. Violence is 100% never the answer. But having a daughter i always want her to feel safe in her being. And god help the person that ever poke the beast inside this little angel.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Channing Tatum on June 18, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person, outdoors and tree.

node.text: What is... I needed to see this today. I love spirals. They means a lot to me. They mean a lot in general. But to me they mean the going in to me deepest self. They remind me that nothing is permanent... nothing. And that’s what makes every moment so beautiful no matter what it IS. Not what i want every moment to be or what it was or could be. But what is right now. Just as it is. It reminds me of nature and how divine i feel it is when I’m in it. I’m not in control of it nor will i will i ever be. I’m just in it and being with it. I’m grateful to be reminded of this today i needed it. And thank you to the people in my life that are my people. My teachers and guide posts. And for all the signs along the way. I’m so grateful

node.text: I have done all kinds of bullshit to get in or stay in shape. Almost everything you can think of. And i have to say nothing yet has been more suffocating and exhausting and effective than freestyle wrestling or open ocean water swimming. There are moments in both that i am always like i think I might die haha. Yup pretty sure i can’t go on let go would be better than this. Haha 😂 and I’m not even i professional athlete. I can’t imagine the depths in which they push themselves. Unreal. I do it for movies Hahahaha very different motivation. Either way get after it everyone. It’s good to be alive. There are so many people that can’t say that. I’m so blessed. P.s as you can see I’m coming in by myself Arin didn’t make it. 2mile ocean swim bruh
